name: Set Pink Tarot Bag & Tarot Cloth for Tarot Cards
description:
Elevate your tarot practice with this beautiful Pink Velvet Tarot Set, thoughtfully designed to protect your sacred deck and enhance your readings.
This enchanting set includes:

Luxurious Pink Velvet Tarot Bag: Crafted from soft, durable velvet, this bag measures 5.4 x 3.6 x 2 inches (13.6 x 9.2 x 5 cm), providing the perfect snug fit and protection for your cherished tarot deck.
High-Quality Pink Celestial Tarot Cloth: Lay out your cards on this exquisite and highly durable cloth, measuring 18 x 18 inches (46 x 46 cm). Its captivating celestial design creates a beautiful and focused space for your spreads, inviting clarity and intuition.
Designed for Your Spiritual Journey:
Whether you're a seasoned reader or just beginning your journey, this set provides a harmonious foundation for your divination practice. The vibrant pink hues and mystical celestial patterns foster a sense of tranquility and connection during your readings.
Fast & Reliable Delivery (USA):
Proudly designed and branded by Tarot Cards Dark Forest, this set benefits from our fast production and delivery process within the USA. Expect your order to be produced and packed within 1-3 business days, with delivery typically arriving in 2-5 business days.
